{"tid":1098786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中環灣仔繞道】東通風大樓抽風系統2月底停運作　路政署今公布","createTime":"2019-04-09T10:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T03:44:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"99c3b343ba73ad0cad20917f5c36dc369d6d90eb","tid":1098786,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"【中環灣仔繞道】東通風大樓抽風系統2月底停運作 路政署今公布<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190409/s00001/1554787265833/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E7%B9%9E%E9%81%93%E3%80%91%E6%9D%B1%E9%80%9A%E9%A2%A8%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E6%8A%BD%E9%A2%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B12%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%81%9C%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190409%2Fs00001%2F1554787265833%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E7%25B9%259E%25E9%2581%2593%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%258A%25BD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B12%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLcwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=06ca7a96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190409%2Fs00001%2F1554787265833%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E7%25B9%259E%25E9%2581%2593%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%258A%25BD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B12%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583&h=23573d17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190409/s00001/1554787265833/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E7%B9%9E%E9%81%93%E3%80%91%E6%9D%B1%E9%80%9A%E9%A2%A8%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E6%8A%BD%E9%A2%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B12%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%81%9C%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83</a><br />\n<br />\n【16:12更新】環保署稱，昨日收到路政署調查報告，而根據初步分析，監測數據顯示空氣質素沒有異常情況。環保署表示，會按法定機制跟進事故，如證據顯示有違規，將按《環境影響評估條例》採取適當行動。<br />\n<br />\n【13:54】1月20日全線啟用的中環及灣仔繞道，路政署今日公布，繞道幹線和其東區走廊連接路（繞道）東通風大樓的空氣淨化系統，2月底有部分用作抽風的風扇組件損壞，東通風大樓空氣淨化系統已暫停運作。路政署稱在上月5日接獲通知，到今早公告事件。<br />\n<br />\n繞道設有三套空氣淨化系統，分佈於東通風大樓、中通風大樓及西通風大樓內。路政署表示，繞道工程顧問公司上月5日通知路政署，承建商2月底發現東通風大樓空氣淨化系統，部分風扇螺絲及扇葉損壞和鬆脫，為安全起見關閉東通風大樓空氣淨化系統。<br />\n<br />\n路政署檢查確認，東通風大樓內15台風扇中有7台損壞，初步懷疑是承建商螺絲裝嵌工序出問題。署方預期，復修工作在4月底完成，並會徹查事件成因及追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n路政署又稱，根據空氣監測數據顯示，繞道隧道內及東隧道口附近一帶近日空氣質素並無異常，署方昨天亦就事件向環保署提交報告。"},{"pid":"7baa32bd8d9d3fb36f31f7a0a3435570f5a97a7e","tid":1098786,"uid":30647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:23:21.000Z","msg":"越嚟越多呢D 隱瞞嘢，隔一個月, 幾個月, 成年先公佈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 個嘢停運，但空氣質素並無異常<br />\n咁唔開個嘢都 ok 啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39673def9a234dedaa1a02855a00aa560ee235fe","tid":1098786,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2dfa50344c70f3bf9c75f2ba3bc73768169ae5e","tid":1098786,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"要香港人吸廢氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反減排撚係咪好鍾意吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db52981265482473054bf1993c266bb01b188e0f","tid":1098786,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc